Text.string: Gonna need a lot of bullets.
Probably not as tough as they look.
Let's see what you got, badass.
We'll see who's got the badder ass.
Just shut up and die already.
Skip the fanfare. I've got work to do.
Just me and my mech against the world!
Let's show 'em what we got, Bear!
Time to teach you a lesson.
Joke's on you, I like pain!
I'll be back on my feet in no time.
Oh, I'm gonna get you for that.
Still got some fight in me!
I'll never get used to that.
Alive again? I can't afford this!
One more time, with a lot less dying.
Hahaha, I'm on a freakin' roll!
Well, would ya look at me.
Ready to go. Let's do it.
Where you been all my life?
That's what I like to see.
[practically drooling] Oh hoh hoh, oh, man.
Well look at you, little lovely.
Now that... is some fine-ass gear.
Ain't making any money standing around like this.
Nope. I'm, uh... I'm good right here... I guess.
Just thinkin' about... getting back to it.
Taking five! [beat] Or six... Or seven...
Guess I should be enjoying this. Ursa Corps never let me stand around for this long.
What is this, guard duty? Let's get moving!
Wasting time... Wasting time... When I SHOULD be wasting bad guys!
Ugh, when I'm not moving, all these thoughts fill my brain, and I'm like, “Lame!” No good can come from that.
[exercise rythym] One, two, three, four, Iron Bear Division Corps. / Five, six, seven, eight, mess starts at nine so don't be late.
[exercise rythym] We'll fight in weather foul or fair, / storms don't mean shit to Iron Bear. / Through the mud and in the night, / I've got my enemy in sight.
Show me what you got, little box.
Hopin' for some good stuff here.
Come on, show me something good!
Good stuff, good stuff, good stuff!
Head to head, me and you.
If you wanna get hurt, sure.
Bet you thought you had me, right?
Care for a change of scenery?
No one told you to stand there.
You want it? You got it!
What is this, a demolition derby now?
Thinkin' it's time to move on.
Maybe we go on foot now?
Smoke, fire -- you got a death wish?
Time to hoof it, I think.
Damn, I gotta lotta good stuff.
What was it again? “Never... eat... sloppy watermelons?”
Yep. That's a good lookin' map.
What KIND of badass should I be?
Should I train in this? Or that?
Hmm. What am I feeling today?
What a crappy way to go...
Can't believe I let them win...
Last of the Corps, goin' out...
Opening up a finely-aged cask of whoop-ass.
Fight for the wrong side? Get dead.
Get good or get dead, scrub.
Oof. That could not have been pleasant.
Need a mop on aisle three!
Hahaha! Your insides are on your outsides now!
Get your ponchos, boys and girls.
I love my big ol' Bear!
Hot damn, I love this mech!
What's that? Couldn't hear you over all this awesome.
Thought you were big shit, but you were just a huge fart!
Huh. Thought that'd be more of a challenge.
I'll take that “badass” title, thank you.
Let me show you what the Ursa Corps can do!
You wanna die? Then stay still!
Come on, back up with ya.
Need you in this fight, soldier.
What? You wanna die in the dirt?
Soldier of fortune, soldier of style.
No makin' heads or tails of this.
Just a bunch of scribbles, as far as I can tell.
Well, that doesn't do me any good.
Get out of what is now my ride!
Ma'am, yes, ma'am! S-sorry, force of habit.
Time to wake up the Bear.
Ah, crap, that's gonna be expensive.
That was my mech, you assholes!
This is why I can't have nice things.
Ohhhh, now you're gonna get it.
Back on my own dumb feet.
Man, and I was finally getting the butt groove the way I like it.
Come on, I, like, JUST got in.
It was just getting good, too.
Aw, come on. Five more minutes.
The murder party continues... on foot.
Stick around and cover me, Bear!
Iron Bear's always got room for you!
And to think that turret was going to waste before.
All aboard the Iron Bear Murder Express!
An Iron Bear built for two!
[dreamily] I love your arms. [snapping out of it] I mean... nice... war we're having, huh?
Think I can make sense of this now.
Can't throw what I don't have.
Ain't got the money for that.
Even Iron Bear can't punch through this stuff.
I think I can get through there now.
Strange. Better do some recon first.
Alien crap, got it. I'll come back later.
Huh. Weird gate... I'll file that under “crap to do later”.
All right, alien gate. Whatcha got for me?
Let's see what weird alien crap's behind this gate.
Just don't send it to the sarge.
I'm down! I don't wanna be down!
